							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/liuhong/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/HONG-Liu-e1726674799827-100x100.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Liu Hong" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/liuhong/">Liu Hong</a></h6>
										Liu Hong is the author of <em>Startling Moon</em> (2002), <em>The Magpie Bridge</em> (2004), <em>The Touch</em> (2006), and <em>Wives of the East Wind</em> (2007), all published by Headline Review. She also co-wrote <em>Nas Folhas do Chá</em>  with Flávia Lins e Silva, published by Zahar (2012). <em>The Good Women of Fudi</em> was published in May 2024 by Scribe.																			</div>
								</div><br class="clear"/><br/>
							</div>
							<br class="clear"/>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div>
													<div class="sidebar_content ad_bottom">
								<li id="custom_ads-24" class="widget Custom_Ads"><div class="htlad-LH_PP_F"></div></li>
							</div>
												<div class="post_wrapper" style="padding-top:0">
							<div class="post_wrapper_inner">
								
															</div>
						</div>
